name: Endless City
description: Endless City; a picture taken on top of a giant tower in the heart of Tokyo. Heard Tokyo is a mega city, but never city lights will fill up entirety of horizon. It was a amazing view up there and I had to take a photo of it. This photo is my contribution to Picetnunc100 movement, first 100 editions will be available and rest will be burned. / Format :: JPEG / Size : 6,000 x 2,919. Collectors will have freedom to print out as personal use at their desire.
